                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " weakens the interlayer AFM coupling so that FM properties gradually develop. Indeed, most studies report a complex metamagnetic behavior in MnBi4Te7 and MnBi6Te10 [21- 27], but a clear FM state only for "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
