                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "A series of EDX (energy- dispersive x- ray spectroscopy) point measurements on individual crystals extracted from the ingot demonstrated a compositional range between Mn: 5.0, B: 36.6, Te: 58.4 and Mn: 4.2, Bi: 37.1, Te: 58.7 (in at. "
